                <h3>The Central Dilemma: Innovation vs. Privacy</h3>
                <p>The integration of technology in learning raises a serious issue of data privacy. While teachers and students benefit from computer-based facilities, they involuntarily relinquish personal information, thus risking exposure.</p>
                
                <h3>Key Challenges</h3>
                <div class="card-container">
