                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Regulatory Complexity</h3>
                        <p>Federal laws such as FERPA, IDEA, and COPPA provide essential privacy safeguards, yet their complexity can result in confusion among educators.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
